<problem id="fs-idm57321696">
<para id="fs-idm63656480">What is [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] in a solution of 0.075 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> HNO<sub>2</sub> and 0.030 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> NaNO<sub>2</sub>?<newline/>
